ðŸ§ª Features
Classifies MRI images into 4 categories of brain tumors

Data preprocessing using ImageDataGenerator

CNN with dropout regularization to prevent overfitting

Evaluation using precision, recall, F1-score, and MSE

Model saved as brain_tumor_classifier.h5
